    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Inferring the date of one thing, as an artifact, a pollen deposit, or a tree ring, from the age of a similar one that has been more firmly dated.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
